reviewText:
I love this movie....My low star rating was because of the false advertisement when buying this movie. On the picture of the packaging of the movie, it says its the Blu-ray AND Digital Copy. However, when I received the movie it was ONLY the blu-ray. The only reason why I purchased this movie on Amazon was because I wanted the combo of the blu-ray and digital copy.

VERY FRUSTRATING!!!
I usually don't complain but the words are not with people talking I loved to be screwed!!!!!!!! Thanks
